-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-weight: 400;\">When you craft a well-thought-out brand—comprised of your skillset, public image, reputation, core beliefs and values; your personality; your vision; and the way you communicate—when all of this is cohesive, clear, and consistent, it will signal to your prospect that it might be of value to keep listening.</span></p>', '2022-01-18 11:05:46', '2022-01-18 13:03:27'),
