 normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: -1rem; line-height: 1; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; display: block;\">Why Lusha?</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Lusha connects you to your most relevant potential customers by creating simple, self-served products that provide access to meaningful and insightful B2B data. We offer ways to leverage data as an enabler for better, smarter and faster conversions at every stage of the customer lifecycle. Lusha was named Top 100 G2 Best Software Company and Top 100 Fastest-Growing product in 2020. Based in the center of Tel Aviv, Israel, Lusha is a fast-growing startup that offers its 110+ employees the opportunity to take an active role in shaping the future of the company. As one of our first hires at the US HQ in Boston, MA, you will be a founding member of the sales team, working with teammates across the globe, While all of us are dedicated to that mission, we surely know how to have a good time.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">On the people side, we believe in creating a caring and fun environment where our employees can be individuals and at the same time, belong to something bigger – the Lushian family. Because ultimately, that’s the key to driving growth for our employees, our company, and our customers. So, if you are customer &amp; impact-focused, thrive in a fast-paced environment, and love working in a place that doesn’t really feel like work, this is your opportunity to become a Lushian and feel the vibes.<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: -1rem; line-height: 1; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; display: block;\">&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: -1rem; line-height: 1; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; display: block;\">﻿</strong>What will you do?</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 3rem; padding-left: 1rem; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\' width=\'10\' height=\'10\' viewBox=\'-1 -1 2 2\'><circle r=\'1\' /></svg>&quot;); color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Proactively reach out to users of the Lusha platform on an outbound basis to nurture, drive adoption, and qualify sales opportunities</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Work closely with the Account Executive team to devise account strategy</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Demonstrate the value of Lusha offerings through phone calls, email, LinkedIn, and other social mediums;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Act as the subject matter expert on Lusha product offerings</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Set appointments and demos for the Lusha sales team when a lead reaches a qualified stage</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">What you bring to the table?</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 3rem; padding-left: 1rem; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\' width=\'10\' height=\'10\' viewBox=\'-1 -1 2 2\'><circle r=\'1\' /></svg>&quot;); color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Intellectual curiosity to understand customer pain points and needs</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Strong and professional communication skills -- written, verbal, presentation</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Ability to persuade, lead, and confidently handle objections</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Strong sense of urgency for reaching goals and key deliverables</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Self-starter mentality: act without being told what to do. Brings new ideas to the company</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Flexibility - things change around here. FAST.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">High integrity, energy, and dedication&nbsp;</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">You are:</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 3rem; padding-left: 1rem; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\' width=\'10\' height=\'10\' viewBox=\'-1 -1 2 2\'><circle r=\'1\' /></svg>&quot;); color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 900;\">Willing to go the extra mile</strong>: Bring a memorable experience and extraordinary value to your clients</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 900;\">Passionate about making an impact</strong>: Do what you do with passion, think about the sale and what’s the best for it</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 900;\">Self-motivated, proactive and entrepreneurial</strong>: We work in a fast-paced environment, with agile methodologies where you will be challenged every day to bring the best solution for your customers and think of new solutions</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 900;\">Great communicator</strong>: The role requires capabilities to explain in different ways the same solution to different people&nbsp;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 900;\">A storyteller</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>- Stories constitute the single most powerful weapon in a salesperson’s arsenal</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 900;\">Ready, able and willing to receive feedback:<span>&nbsp;</span></strong>The BDR has tremendous growth potential and should be coachable and eager to learn</li></ul>', '2022-01-19 07:12:07', '2022-01-19 08:03:42');
INSERT INTO `careers` (`id`, `image`, `career_title`, `career_category`, `career_location`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(4, 'jobs.png', 'Competitive Intelligence Manager', 'Marketing', 'Tel Aviv', '<h4 class=\"description__title description__title-main\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Description</h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">We’re looking for an exceptional competitive intelligence manager to join our Product Marketing team. You will make an impact through ownership of the competitive landscape research, and have direct influence on our sales and marketing competitive strategies and product development efforts. This dynamic position is an incredible opportunity for a talented expert who thrives on research, deep understanding of the business and its landscape and knows how to provide actionable and data-driven insights .&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: -1rem; line-height: 1; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; display: block;\">You will:</strong></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 3rem; padding-left: 1rem; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\' width=\'10\' height=\'10\' viewBox=\'-1 -1 2 2\'><circle r=\'1\' /></svg>&quot;); color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Use first-hand knowledge and available research sources to identify market trends and advise the company leadership on product and go-to-market strategies.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Be the undisputed expert of the competition’s products and services and their latest product releases.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Define and develop an accurate representation of Lusha’s different personas.&nbsp;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Have an understanding of business intelligence tools and keep current on those tools and trends.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Brief stakeholders on competitor technologies, competitive messaging and fixing positioning issues</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Collaborate with the rest of the product marketing team on the creation of competitive positioning and collateral for other teams and departments.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: -1rem; line-height: 1; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; display: block;\">You are:</strong></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 3rem; padding-left: 1rem; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\' width=\'10\' height=\'10\' viewBox=\'-1 -1 2 2\'><circle r=\'1\' /></svg>&quot;); color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 900;\">A curious investigator. You love exploring and know how to communicate your findings to senior management and decision makers, and translate your insights into a clear and constructive action plan.&nbsp;</strong></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 900;\">Passionate about technology. You are keen to learn about how things work and are able to explain technical concepts in ways that everyday people can understand.</strong></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 900;\">Highly analytical and data-oriented.<span>&nbsp;</span></strong>You are able to thoroughly investigate an industry from all angles and a variety of sources and identify the important trends and insights.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 900;\">Focused and strategic.<span>&nbsp;</span></strong>You know how to look at the big picture, ask the right questions in a sea of endless information, and “separate the rocks from the sand”.&nbsp;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 900;\">Organized.<span>&nbsp;</span></strong>You are able to manage highly interdependent, multifaceted projects and keep various workstreams on track - even those with many moving parts.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-