svg\' width=\'10\' height=\'10\' viewBox=\'-1 -1 2 2\'><circle r=\'1\' /></svg>&quot;); color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Experience with distributed systems</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">1+ years of experience using React.js, Vue or Angular</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Experience with RabbitMQ/SQS/Kafka</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Experience with Kubernetes &amp; dockers</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Have contributed to open-source projects.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;\">Experience in Test Driven Development (TDD) and Continuous Delivery</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: -1rem; line-height: 1; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; display: block;\">Why Lusha?</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Lusha connects you to your most relevant potential customers by creating simple, self-served products that provide access to meaningful and insightful B2B data. We offer ways to leverage data as an enabler for better, smarter and faster conversions at every stage of the customer lifecycle. Lusha was named Top 100 G2 Best Software Company and Top 100 Fastest-Growing product in 2020. Based in the center of Tel Aviv, Lusha is a fast-growing startup that offers its 110+ employees the opportunity to take an active role in shaping the future of the company. While all of us are dedicated to that mission, we surely know how to have a good time.</p>', '2022-01-19 07:15:35', '2022-01-19 08:04:25');
