(6, 'web-programming.png', 'Core - Backend Team Leader', 'R&D', 'Tel Aviv', '<h4 class=\"description__title description__title-main\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Description</h4><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Lusha is growing and we are looking for an experienced backend infrastructure team leader to join our team.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">If you are an experienced team leader, leading a core or infrastructure team in web technologies, you are passionate about enabling developers to run faster, secure, and more accurately, you have great communications skills, are highly motivated and eager to create an impact, continue reading cause this may very well be what you are looking for!</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: -1rem; line-height: 1; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; display: block;\">What will you be doing?</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">As R&amp;D team leader of the infrastructure team, you will be working with your team to enable others to run faster, secure and accurately by maximizing their effort to reach the goals of the company. You will be challenged to solve complex problems by designing and implementing solutions while working closely with the Architecture team, DevOps and software engineers.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit