(9, 'human-resources.png', 'Organizational Development Director', 'HR', 'India', '<h4 class=\"description__title description__title-main\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Description</h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">We’re looking for a seasoned OD director to join our HR team. You will make an impact through design and creating the infrastructure for our culture. This strategic position is an incredible opportunity for a manager who wants to impact talent and culture in our company, who thrives on creating engaging and innovative journeys for our people</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: -1rem; line-height: 1; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; display: block;\">Why Lusha?</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Lusha connects you to your most relevant potential customers by creating simple, self-served products that provide access to meaningful and insightful B2B data. We offer ways to leverage data as an enabler for better, smarter and faster conversions at every stage of the customer lifecycle.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Lusha was named Top 100 G2 Best Software Company and Top 100 Fastest-Growing product in 2020. As a fast-growing startup in Tel Aviv (We grew from 110 to 240 in 2021), Lusha provides its employees with a chance to take an active part in shaping the company\'s future. While all of us are dedicated to that mission, we surely know how to have a good time.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(21, 20, 23); font-family: Circular, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-s